Package: brcrimR
Title: Downloads Brazilian Criminal Information
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Fernando", "Corrêa", email = "fcorrea@abjur.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("José", "de Jesus", email = "jjesusfilho@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: Brazillian security departments maintains several sources of criminal information. Very often, those sources are not user friendly, specially when building historical databases. This packages provides a tidy and (almost) unified framework for accessing those information. 
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
